content.rendered:
Directed by Kaarthikk Sundar

Written by Tharun Bhascker. Deepak Sundarrajan. Sanjeev. Kaarthikk Sundar

Star Harish Kalyan. Abishek Kumar. Anish Kuruvilla. Ashwin Kumar Lakshmikanthan. Abdool Lee. Priya Bhavani Shankar. Sawkar Siddhanth (Chef Siddhanth (Siddhanth Sawkar)). Tharani SureshKumar. Anbu Thasan. Samyuktha Viswanathan

Language Tamil

Producers Satyanarayana Koneru. Naren. Ramesh Varma

Production A Studios. Madhav Media. SP Cinemas
